---
/**
 * ai-agents · 0005 · Figure 5 — the agent loop (observe/think/act) plus the
 * runtime stop-conditions panel. Verbatim from the source HTML.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 620 250"
        role="img"
        aria-label="The agent loop on the left with observe, think, act stages, and a runtime stop-conditions panel on the right listing the conditions that end the loop"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <!-- the loop -->
            <text
                x="135"
                y="18"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#6b675f"
                letter-spacing=".05em">THE LOOP (model)</text
            >
            <rect x="80" y="34" width="110" height="38" rx="8" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text
                x="135"
                y="57"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">Observe</text
            >
            <line
                x1="135"
                y1="72"
                x2="135"
                y2="98"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <rect
                x="80"
                y="100"
                width="110"
                height="38"
                rx="8"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect><text
                x="135"
                y="123"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Think</text
            >
            <line
                x1="135"
                y1="138"
                x2="135"
                y2="164"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <rect
                x="80"
                y="166"
                width="110"
                height="38"
                rx="8"
                fill="#eef5ee"
                stroke="#2f5d3a"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect><text
                x="135"
                y="189"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">Act (tool)</text
            >
            <!-- back-edge -->
            <path
                d="M190,185 L232,185 L232,53 L190,53"
                fill="none"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></path>
            <text
                x="248"
                y="122"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="9"
                fill="#6b675f"
                transform="rotate(90 248 122)">next step</text
            >
            <!-- gate arrow to runtime -->
            <line
                x1="190"
                y1="119"
                x2="300"
                y2="119"
                stroke="#9a2417"
                stroke-width="1.6"
                marker-end="url(#arwR)"></line>
            <text x="245" y="111" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#9a2417"
                >every step checked</text
            >
            <!-- runtime panel -->
            <rect
                x="302"
                y="28"
                width="308"
                height="214"
                rx="10"
                fill="#fbf7ea"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="456"
                y="48"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">RUNTIME STOP CONDITIONS</text
            >
            <text x="318" y="74" font-size="9.5" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >&#10003; model emits final answer (no tool call)</text
            >
            <text x="318" y="94" font-size="9.5" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >&#10003; explicit done / submit tool called</text
            >
            <text x="318" y="114" font-size="9.5" fill="#2f5d3a"
                >&#10003; external verifier passes (tests/schema)</text
            >
            <line x1="316" y1="124" x2="596" y2="124" stroke="#e3dcc6" stroke-width="1"></line>
            <text x="318" y="144" font-size="9.5" fill="#9a2417"
                >&#10007; step cap hit (e.g. 20)</text
            >
            <text x="318" y="164" font-size="9.5" fill="#9a2417">&#10007; wall-clock timeout</text>
            <text x="318" y="184" font-size="9.5" fill="#9a2417"
                >&#10007; token / $ budget exhausted</text
            >
            <text x="318" y="204" font-size="9.5" fill="#9a2417"
                >&#10007; repetition detected (same call &times;N)</text
            >
            <text x="318" y="224" font-size="9.5" fill="#9a2417"
                >&#10007; human interrupt / HITL halt</text
            >
            <text
                x="456"
                y="238"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="8.5"
                font-style="italic"
                fill="#6b675f">&#10007; exits = halt + escalate, never silent</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        The model proposes continuing or stopping; the runtime <em>decides</em>. Green = legitimate
        completion (and verify it). Red = safety stops that must exist independently of the model's
        judgment.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
